PrecisAuthority to sign a SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between THE MISHKOSIIMIINIIZIIBING FIRST NATION, THE ANISHINAABEG OF ONIGAMING FIRST NATION and the Province of ONTARIO for the purpose of resolving a specific claim related to the setting apart, under the terms of Treaty No. 3 [the North-West Angle Treaty], of some 1,600 acres of land fronting on Lake of Woods that were transferred to the Province in 1931 without having first obtained a proper surrender from the Bands in question.
